To get the present directory type 
pwd
for calender use
cal
cal feb 2011
cal 12 1993

for date use
date

for formatting date in your style use
date '+DATE:%m-%y%nTime:%H:%M:%S'


for making a folder use
mkdir folder_name

mkdir Desktop/folder_name

touch file1 file2 file3
to make empty text files


use cat command to make files
cat > file_name/existing file
type somethin
press 
cat tutorial1 > tutorial2
ctrl + D to exit



mv to rename the file
mv file1 file2



rm to remove/delete files
rm file1 

rm -r newDir 
or
rmdir newDir


link 
ln old new (hard link) //from now on changes you made to old file woll get automatically reflected in new file //hard link is a file..

ln -s old_file old_soft (soft link)  // shortcut 



